snippet.title: Tannenberg 1914-1918 I Steam Early Access Release Announcement
snippet.description:
Grab your shashka and get ready for a winter offensive – Tannenberg launches  November 16 on Steam Early Access!

Tannenberg is the latest entry in the 1914-1918 WW1 Game series of FPS games which started with Verdun. The game takes place on the Eastern Front and will be available later this year on PC via Steam Early Access. 

Make sure to add the game to your wishlist:  http://store.steampowered.com/app/633460
